        <abstract> 
<p>Oliver has written able paper on dimorphism for <hi rend="italic">Natural History Review</hi> [n.s. 2 (1862): 235–43].</p>  
<p>CD’s account of <hi rend="italic">Viola</hi> is novel and interesting.</p> 
            <p>Has finished Cameroon mountain plants.</p>
            <p>Jury work at exhibition.</p>
            <p>Domestic problems – wife is ill, no cook, etc.</p>
